    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed and built by a team of veterans from Activision, WB Games, Crytek, Epic and Guerilla Games, ANIMO Stars Arena is a game that blends adorable animal pilots with ridiculously powerful mech juggernauts, in epic battles and evolving battlescapes that will keep you constantly rebuilding your loadouts and hangar of fully customized war machines!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras/77f68994ac62d59ccb2b1ee4b0f3beac.avif?t=1749525024\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras_big/77f68994ac62d59ccb2b1ee4b0f3beac.avif?t=1749525024 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR MECH</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each ANIMO is composed of a: Cabin, Engine, Bumper, and 2 weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your own mech war machines and wreak havoc in multiple battlescapes. Choose traversal engines spanning treads, hovercraft, spider legs, wheels and more, and pair them with dozens of cabins and bumpers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then finish off your personalized mech with a host of special weapons like grappling hooks, flamethrower, sniper rifle, lasers, and more to manifest your own incredibly cute and powerful mechs of annihilation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras/cd040f69c025cd2ba7ef3e21a4038ed1.avif?t=1749525024\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras_big/cd040f69c025cd2ba7ef3e21a4038ed1.avif?t=1749525024 width=800 height=1000 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras/ed8672e4518868217989c4d3ead11216.avif?t=1749525024\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras_big/ed8672e4518868217989c4d3ead11216.avif?t=1749525024 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PAINT YOUR ANIMO!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of paint themes and skins for your mech!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras/971f835f4ff37cf0c0209bc1e3db9f83.avif?t=1749525024\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras_big/971f835f4ff37cf0c0209bc1e3db9f83.avif?t=1749525024 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR PILOT!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your pilot represents who you are. Choose your favorite pilot whether that’s a cute cuddly puppy, a fierce bird, or a slithering snake!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras/7b2e0986022980ebd5bb6b842443093f.avif?t=1749525024\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras_big/7b2e0986022980ebd5bb6b842443093f.avif?t=1749525024 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras/91b7bed07b3ef9628a0d667bdd0c3358.avif?t=1749525024\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras_big/91b7bed07b3ef9628a0d667bdd0c3358.avif?t=1749525024 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAY YOUR FAVORITE GAME MODE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump on board your ANIMO and battle other players across different game modes including team deathmatch, battle royale, capture the flag and more!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras/c0b8ce0e88419eea6582900b32e3df3e.poster.avif?t=1749525024\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras/c0b8ce0e88419eea6582900b32e3df3e.webm?t=1749525024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323240/extras/c0b8ce0e88419eea6582900b32e3df3e.mp4?t=1749525024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
